outputs.output_descr: The project covers the support that the Operational Unit for Development Assistance (OUDA) by the Prime Minister Decree No. 1752, issued in the year 2003, and provides to the various Ministries in the implementation of capacity building projects funded by bilaterial donors that fall within the mandate of UNDP.

project_descr: Project Implementation Services by the Operational Unit for Development Assistance (OUDA)
project_title: Project Implementation Services by Opert.Unit for Dev.As
